\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Caption

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Pseudo-code representing the step set 
\begin_inset Formula $SS_{1}$
\end_inset

, which is applied by the agents in areas with service coverage.
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "alg:07-Agent_step_set_1"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


